==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nailer
<hw>Nail"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One whose
occupation is to make nails; a nail maker.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who fastens with, or drives, nails.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Naileress</ent>⟦br⟧
